com.google.gcloud.bigquery

Class Dataset

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gcloud.bigquery.Dataset

  • public final class Dataset
extends Object
    A Google BigQuery Dataset.

    Objects of this class are immutable. Operations that modify the dataset like update(com.google.gcloud.bigquery.DatasetInfo, com.google.gcloud.bigquery.BigQuery.DatasetOption...) return a new object. To get a Dataset object with the most recent information use reload(com.google.gcloud.bigquery.BigQuery.DatasetOption...).
